room_title: Escape room "Island Paradise" by Vector Escape Games in Redlands
room_address: 1765 Orange Tree Lane Unit B Redlands CA 92374
room_description: Pack your bags and grab your snorkels - you’re going on a trip to a tropical island! Oops, it looks like someone sent you to the wrong island and the locals don’t look too friendly. Take an unplanned adventure in saving yourself and hopefully your friends before everyone appears on the dinner menu!
